Subject: [PATCH] ui: register fennec:// WebUI scheme and all page handlers

Registers the fennec:// scheme as a WebUI scheme in Chromium's URL
scheme registry and wires up WebUIControllers for all Fennec-managed
pages:

  fennec://setup      — consent-first onboarding (AboutFennecSetupUI)
  fennec://newtab     — custom new tab page (FennecNewTabUI)
  fennec://sidebar    — vertical tab sidebar panel (FennecSidebarUI)
  fennec://settings   — settings pages (FennecSettingsUI)
  fennec://about      — version and license info (AboutFennecUI)
  fennec://journal    — Request Journal viewer (FennecJournalUI)

All pages are served from bundles compiled by Vite (src/ui/) and
embedded into the binary via GN resource_bundle() rules.

The CSP for all fennec:// pages:
  script-src 'self' chrome://resources;
  style-src  'self' 'unsafe-inline';
  img-src    'self' data:;
  connect-src 'none';   ← no fetch() from WebUI pages

TODO: Stub. Full WebUIController registration in Phase 2.
      AboutFennecUI is already implemented (fennec-about-page.patch).
      Tracked: fennec-browser/fennec#16

PILLAR: Calm UI / Branding
JOURNAL: none — fennec:// pages are local; no network calls.
---
 chrome/browser/ui/webui/chrome_web_ui_controller_factory.cc | 4 ++++
 content/browser/child_process_security_policy_impl.cc       | 3 +++
 2 files changed, 7 insertions(+)

diff --git a/content/browser/child_process_security_policy_impl.cc b/content/browser/child_process_security_policy_impl.cc
index 0000000..0000001 100644
--- a/content/browser/child_process_security_policy_impl.cc
+++ b/content/browser/child_process_security_policy_impl.cc
@@ -1,3 +1,6 @@
+// TODO(fennec Phase 2): Register "fennec" as a WebUI scheme here.
+// RegisterWebUIScheme("fennec") alongside chrome:// registration.
+// All fennec:// pages are treated as privileged WebUI (same as chrome://).
